<p>Between high school and college, I was one of three developers at MeringCarson, a small but loud branding/design/marking firm in San Diego. I got my hands very dirty with front end technologies and PHP creating a custom content management system and making pixel-perfect versions of Photoshop designs.</p>
<p><b>Tech: PHP, JavaScript, HTML/SASS</b>
